annotationA: Mitochondrial DNA helicase; ATP binding; single-stranded DNA binding; 5'-3' DNA helicase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitochondrial genome maintenance; protein homooligomerization; mitochondrial DNA replication
annotationB: Single-stranded DNA-binding protein, mitochondrial; This protein binds preferentially and cooperatively to pyrimidine rich ss-DNA. Required for mitochondrial DNA replication
